When specifying the `AutoPublishAlias` field for a Function, CloudFormation will delete all aliases that are not the specified in the single field.

Upon pull request, we'd like to deploy to a "Staging" environment, by creating an alias named "Staging", and an APIGateway Stage named "Staging", and have them point them at each other.
